Text.string: Time to take out the trash!
I'll have to melt you down!
Just get back from the MESS hall?
Scrub the guy that thinks he's fly!
Hey, a witch with no broom!
Time to get back to work.
Out with the old, I guess.
So fresh and so clean, clean!
Scrub scrub here, scrub scrub there...
Let's put you to good use!
It's a dirty job, and I love it!
I'm the boss of you, got it?
Do as I say, not as I do!
It's my duty to trash that booty!
See which way the wind's blowing?
I'll dispose of this for you!
Nice catch! Why, thank you! Oh, you're quite welcome.
Put your trash in the proper receptacle!
Out of sight, out of mind.
What you can't see can probably still hurt you.
I'll get you for that! Whenever you're back!
Pick up when you're done, not now!
I guess I'll clean up after that thing.
Well, how do you like that?
My only love sprung from my only hate!
Get down here and be trash!
You look like trash waiting to happen.
Reminds me of the junk yard.
Guess I've gotta clean THAT up now!
Come on! It's trash CAN, not trash CAN'T!
But there's still so much to clean!
If there's time to lean, there's time to clean!
How would you feel if I did that?
I hope it's clean where I'm goin'.
Uh-uh! Not on my clean floors you don't!
Oh, I can smell you from here!
You're going out with the trash!
[singsong] Makin' a mess, so I can clean it later.
Aw, come on! They're mopping the floor with us!
I'm not cleaning this up! Okay fine, I am.
Whoa! They're on a hot streak!
Come on, somebody should stop them!
Get that dirt off MY shoulder!
